sentences: He passed the audition, and played Paul McCartney in the show between 1978 and 1983.
In 1994 he was asked to join the band as bassist and vocalist, and subsequently appeared on the band's Illuminations and Live in Geneva albums.
In 1997, Kishman left Wishbone Ash to pursue different musical projects.
Kishman is now a current band member with the critically acclaimed Classical Mystery Tour.
